  note right of Intervention
  Represents a planned activity, stimulus, or interaction
  aimed at influencing user behavior or collecting data.
  Examples: questionnaires, prompts, mini-games, etc.
  end note

  class Questionnaire {
    +questionCount: int
    +estimatedTime: int
